bill_title: revise certain programs regarding the Department of Game, Fish and Parks.

bill_versions.bill_text: FOR AN ACT ENTITLED, An Act to revise certain programs regarding the Department of Game, Fish and Parks. BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF SOUTH DAKOTA: Section 1. That the code be amended by adding a NEW SECTION to read: That programs regarding the Department of Game, Fish and Parks are revised. 100 copies were printed on recycled paper by the South Dakota Legislative Research Council at a cost of $.167 per page. . Insertions into existing statutes are indicated by underscores. Deletions from existing statutes are indicated by overstrikes.
